reviewText: I've seen this on TV twice over a couple of years. These were all wonderful, funny, mature women telling about how they still experienced sexuality over 65. Done well and quite tasteful. I'd watch it a 3rd time for sure if it was on TV. Too bad I can't order the DVD. The mystery if "old" people are "still doing it" is being unravelled. No more mysteries about this subject. GOOD!!
